column5: YEP NICE FINISH.  Going to be a great 2 races. Sorry to see you took Kyle.
Ha, nope, thank the Lord I did not, whew!!!
I love how NASCAR handled Kyle after Friday nights Bull. As for the chase I'll be happy with either Tony or Carl as they are both deserving.
They need to do that more often.No matter the driver.
I PRV'd the race, successfully avoided watching highlights, and then log on to OFC for some fishing stuff.  Safe right?  AAAARGHHHHHHHH!!!!!!!!!!  And what's worse, I'm an Edwards fan.  (
id love to see carl take it, can only imagine how big the classic backflip off the roof of the car would be after winning it all haha

Ya, I'm pulling for Edward too.  I wish he had won more races this year, though.  Tony's won 4 times so even if Carl DOES win the chase, there's one part of me that says Tony deserves it more.  Oh well, next races are gonna be crazy!
Sorry about that Mike - oops!   Get with the real world time will ya     YUP
Hah hah hah!  That's not the first time I've been accused of being in a time warp, Joey!
Can he make it 3 in a row? I hope so.
Im just happy its someone other than Jimmie this year LOL   .  Although what he did was pretty remarkable.
